h\u1ea9u trang m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y!<\/strong><\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"620\" data-end=\"623\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"682\"><strong data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"680\">\u00a0MASKNE \u2013 V\u00cc SAO DA B\u1eca M\u1ee4N KHI \u0110EO KH\u1ea8U TRANG?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"684\" data-end=\"955\"><strong data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"788\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y ra Maskne l\u00e0 do l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 h\u01a1i \u1ea9m t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean da<\/strong>. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, <strong data-start=\"834\" data-end=\"879\">d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn, m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t ra ngo\u00e0i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng <strong data-start=\"925\" data-end=\"952\">m\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"957\" data-end=\"1483\"><strong data-start=\"960\" data-end=\"997\">C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb Maskne:<\/strong><br data-start=\"997\" data-end=\"1000\" \/><strong data-start=\"1002\" data-end=\"1027\">&#8211; B\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng:<\/strong> Kh\u1ea9u trang gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<br data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1120\" \/><strong data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1144\">&#8211; H\u01a1i \u1ea9m t\u1eeb h\u01a1i th\u1edf:<\/strong> L\u00e0m t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m tr\u00ean da, t\u1ea1o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n sinh s\u00f4i.<br data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1227\" \/><strong data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1249\">&#8211; Ma s\u00e1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c:<\/strong> B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u1ea9u trang c\u1ecd x\u00e1t v\u00e0o da, g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, vi\u00eam da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<br data-start=\"1342\" data-end=\"1345\" \/><strong data-start=\"1347\" data-end=\"1377\">&#8211; Kh\u1ea9u trang k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:<\/strong> M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ea9u trang t\u00e1i ch\u1ebf ch\u1ee9a <strong data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1438\">ch\u1ea5t h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i<\/strong>, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb b\u00ed b\u00e1ch h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1485\" data-end=\"1570\"><strong data-start=\"1488\" data-end=\"1568\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh Maskne, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u1ea9u trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p!<\/strong><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1485\" data-end=\"1570\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/scontent.fhan3-3.fna.fbcdn.net\/v\/t39.30808-6\/461156851_949578000527569_7663881115197719037_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s1080x2048_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=127cfc&amp;_nc_ohc=9Pen2xscNNwQ7kNvgGOFGZ4&amp;_nc_oc=AdikMY8BOSKcCw60BAcJ2c-S9W7kakow5QRFaUWQCKfitAlt_eVjmPcVH1YiBmrFC0I&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhan3-3.fna&amp;_nc_gid=AaKcYz1EmXpg2igbqQC49Fn&amp;oh=00_AYD23axWKbH2gs71RtW6fuFyRJz2HqF-12msGoSNGrurqQ&amp;oe=67BCE251\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh.\" \/><\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1572\" data-end=\"1575\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1577\" data-end=\"1635\"><strong data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1633\">\u00a0GI\u1ea2I PH\u00c1P NG\u0102N NG\u1eeaA &amp; \u0110I\u1ec0U TR\u1eca MASKNE HI\u1ec6U QU\u1ea2<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1637\" data-end=\"1695\"><span style=\"font-size: 150%;\"><strong data-start=\"1640\" data-end=\"1693\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea9u trang kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1697\" data-end=\"1811\">\ud83d\udca1 <strong data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1724\">KH\u1ea8U TR